verse.lines:
{lang-eng}I need Thee, oh, I need Thee;
Every hour I need Thee;
Oh, bless me now, my Savior!
I come to Thee.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}I need Thee every hour,
Most gracious Lord;
No tender voice like Thine
Can peace afford.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}I need Thee every hour,
Stay Thou near by;
Temptations lose their power
When Thou art nigh.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}I need Thee every hour,
In joy or pain;
Come quickly and abide,
Or life is vain.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}I need Thee every hour,
Teach me Thy will;
And Thy rich promises
In me fulfill.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}I need Thee every hour,
Most Holy One;
Oh, make me Thine indeed,
Thou blessed Son.{/lang-eng}
